message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs and expectations. This product holds significant value for you at $150, just like it does for me. Considering its quality and the benefits it provides, I would like to extend this opportunity to you at an exclusive price of $145. I believe this offer presents a great chance for both of us to benefit. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
